() show newline
(Hardware entropy \(RDRAND/RDSEED\) feeds the OS pool. Quantum RNG \(ID) show newline
(Quantique, drand beacons\) planned for Phase 3+.) show newline
() show newline
(There are NO EXCEPTIONS. Never use:) show newline
() show newline
(  * \(chicken random\) - Uses Mersenne Twister, not cryptographically secure) show newline
(  * srfi-27 - Statistical randomness, not cryptographic) show newline
(  * /dev/urandom directly - Platform-specific, misses getrandom\(2\) benefits) show newline
(  * arc4random_buf\(\) directly - Use libsodium's abstraction) show newline
(  * Custom PRNGs - Unaudited, likely insecure) show newline
() show newline
(The only approved functions are from crypto-ffi:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    \(random-bytes n\)         ; n cryptographically random bytes) show newline
(    \(random-u8\)              ; random byte [0, 255]) show newline
(    \(random-u32\)             ; random 32-bit unsigned) show newline
(    \(random-uniform limit\)   ; uniform [0, limit\) with rejection sampling) show newline
