(BOOT-TIME FIPS TESTING) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(Trust but verify. Every entropy source MUST be tested at boot time with) show newline
(FIPS 140-2 statistical tests on 20,000 bits \(2500 bytes\):) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Monobit Test) show newline
(------------) show newline
() show newline
(Count of 1-bits must be 9654 < n < 10346 \(within 3.43σ of expected) show newline
(10000\).) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    \(fips-monobit-test bytes\)  ; Pass if balanced) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Poker Test) show newline
(----------) show newline
() show newline
(Distribution of 4-bit nibbles must be uniform. X = \(16/5000\) × Σf² -) show newline
(5000 must satisfy 1.03 < X < 57.4.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    \(fips-poker-test bytes\)   ; Pass if nibbles distributed) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Runs Test) show newline
(---------) show newline
() show newline
(Runs of consecutive 0s and 1s must fall within bounds:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(  Run Length  Expected Range \(each bit value\)  ) show newline
(  1           2267-2733                        ) show newline
(  2           1079-1421                        ) show newline
(  3           502-748                          ) show newline
(  4           223-402                          ) show newline
(  5           90-223                           ) show newline
(  6+          90-223                           ) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    \(fips-runs-test bytes\)    ; Pass if run distribution normal) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Long Run Test) show newline
(-------------) show newline
() show newline
(No run of 26 or more consecutive identical bits.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    \(fips-long-run-test bytes\) ; Pass if no pathological runs) show newline
() show newline
(Implementation in fips.scm:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    \(define \(test-randomness\)) show newline
(      "FIPS 140-2 randomness tests on 20,000 bits.") show newline
(      \(let* \(\(sample \(random-bytes 2500\)\)) show newline
(             \(bytes \(blob->u8vector sample\)\)\)) show newline
(        \(and \(fips-monobit-test bytes\)) show newline
(             \(fips-poker-test bytes\)) show newline
(             \(fips-runs-test bytes\)) show newline
(             \(fips-long-run-test bytes\)\)\)\)) show newline
(    ;; Called at REPL boot and by forge module load) show newline
(    \(unless \(test-randomness\)) show newline
(      \(error "Entropy source failed FIPS 140-2 tests"\)\)) show newline
